00:01:23,550 --> 00:01:26,980
=Battle Through The Heaven=

18
00:01:27,020 --> 00:01:29,980
=Episode 29=

19
00:01:30,440 --> 00:01:32,160
Master Fei? Well...

20
00:01:32,950 --> 00:01:34,160
Am I seeing things?

21
00:01:34,800 --> 00:01:36,040
Our Wind Thunder Hall

22
00:01:36,190 --> 00:01:39,000
was the first in Central Plains
to join forces

23
00:01:39,000 --> 00:01:42,510
with Starfall Hall against the Hall of Souls.

24
00:01:42,680 --> 00:01:44,230
We have more reasons to be here

25
00:01:44,360 --> 00:01:45,910
than any other faction.

26
00:01:46,480 --> 00:01:47,320
The first?

27
00:01:48,440 --> 00:01:49,870
Am I hearing correctly?

28
00:01:50,800 --> 00:01:53,510
Back then, when Wind Sage called for
an attack on the Hall of Souls

29
00:01:53,590 --> 00:01:54,630
to save Master Yao,

30
00:01:54,950 --> 00:01:57,910
you seemed to be the first to refuse.

31
00:01:59,480 --> 00:02:01,160
Feng Qing'er from our hall

32
00:02:01,310 --> 00:02:04,440
has fought against the Hall of Souls.

33
00:02:04,910 --> 00:02:06,480
Regarding Master Yao's matter,

34
00:02:06,480 --> 00:02:08,600
our Wind Thunder Hall contributed.

35
00:02:09,520 --> 00:02:10,360
Sword Sage,

36
00:02:10,880 --> 00:02:11,960
it seems we lose

37
00:02:11,960 --> 00:02:13,550
because we don't have a disobedient disciple

38
00:02:13,910 --> 00:02:15,390
to help us gain glory.

39
00:02:16,830 --> 00:02:18,880
- Master!
- What are you two talking about?

40
00:02:19,000 --> 00:02:19,910
- Today I'll...
- Enough.

41
00:02:19,910 --> 00:02:20,830
- Let go of me!
- Come on.

42
00:02:21,160 --> 00:02:22,880
How could you two say that?

43
00:02:22,880 --> 00:02:23,720
What are you doing?

44
00:02:24,390 --> 00:02:25,790
- Put my master down!
- What are you doing?

45
00:02:25,800 --> 00:02:26,960
Come back! What are you doing?

46
00:02:27,110 --> 00:02:27,960
Put my master down!

47
00:02:27,960 --> 00:02:30,090
- Two rascals and two old rascals!
- Come on. Please calm down.

48
00:02:30,520 --> 00:02:31,470
Let go!

49
00:02:31,470 --> 00:02:32,800
- Master.
- Let go!

50
00:02:53,080 --> 00:02:53,920
Stop!

51
00:03:00,190 --> 00:03:02,960
Today, we gather at Starfall Hall

52
00:03:03,520 --> 00:03:05,600
to deal with a common enemy.

53
00:03:06,600 --> 00:03:08,630
Since it's an alliance, let's start anew

54
00:03:09,320 --> 00:03:11,800
and let go of past grievances.

55
00:03:13,270 --> 00:03:14,750
Central Plains stands together,

56
00:03:14,910 --> 00:03:17,240
and from now on, we are all on the same side.

57
00:03:19,720 --> 00:03:20,800
An alliance is feasible,

58
00:03:22,030 --> 00:03:23,000
but who will

59
00:03:23,240 --> 00:03:24,110
be the leader?

60
00:03:24,960 --> 00:03:26,190
The position of the leader

61
00:03:26,750 --> 00:03:28,270
must be held by someone with

62
00:03:28,440 --> 00:03:29,880
strong strength and a high reputation.

63
00:03:31,360 --> 00:03:33,830
I am not suitable for this position.

64
00:03:35,270 --> 00:03:36,240
Master Fei,

65
00:03:36,440 --> 00:03:38,880
although powerful, is a bit hot-tempered

66
00:03:39,160 --> 00:03:40,880
and may act impulsively,

67
00:03:41,320 --> 00:03:42,440
not suitable for the leader's role.

68
00:03:43,830 --> 00:03:46,030
Shadow Domain Sage, you are talking too much.

69
00:03:48,720 --> 00:03:51,240
I think that Master Yao is the most suitable.

70
00:03:51,830 --> 00:03:52,670
No, no,

71
00:03:53,000 --> 00:03:53,910
I'm too old.

72
00:03:54,830 --> 00:03:57,030
This alliance was Xiao Yan's idea.

73
00:03:58,720 --> 00:03:59,560
I propose that

74
00:03:59,960 --> 00:04:02,670
we don't need to stick to formalities.

75
00:04:03,360 --> 00:04:05,930
Central Plains' rise depends on the strength
of the younger generation.

76
00:04:07,030 --> 00:04:08,960
Let's choose the leader from them.

77
00:04:12,720 --> 00:04:13,860
Among the younger generation,

78
00:04:13,880 --> 00:04:16,000
Xiao Yan is naturally the most suitable.

79
00:04:17,550 --> 00:04:18,390
He's a peak Dou Venerate

80
00:04:18,830 --> 00:04:19,970
with four Heavenly Flames

81
00:04:20,200 --> 00:04:22,310
and experience in fighting against the
Hall of Souls,

82
00:04:22,440 --> 00:04:23,510
no one is more suitable than him.

83
00:04:26,160 --> 00:04:27,000
I agree.

84
00:04:28,070 --> 00:04:28,910
I also agree.

85
00:04:30,880 --> 00:04:31,720
I agree too.

86
00:04:34,880 --> 00:04:37,790
Xiao Yan is the direct disciple of Yao Chen,

87
00:04:39,070 --> 00:04:42,830
and he is more capable
than the First Disciple.

88
00:04:43,000 --> 00:04:45,040
He is indeed an ideal choice.

89
00:04:45,480 --> 00:04:46,950
Mu Qingluan is also not bad.

90
00:04:47,640 --> 00:04:48,600
He and Feng Qing'er

91
00:04:49,000 --> 00:04:50,600
will also be the backbone of the alliance.

92
00:04:52,950 --> 00:04:53,950
Bad news!

93
00:04:54,670 --> 00:04:55,510
Bad news!

94
00:04:55,600 --> 00:04:57,600
There is an intruder in the back mountain.

95
00:04:58,510 --> 00:04:59,670
I know who this person is.

96
00:05:00,830 --> 00:05:01,830
He is one of us.

97
00:05:03,350 --> 00:05:04,190
Move!

98
00:05:06,760 --> 00:05:07,720
Masters,

99
00:05:08,230 --> 00:05:09,440
he was sneakily moving ten boxes

100
00:05:09,480 --> 00:05:10,670
of gold coins to the back mountain.

101
00:05:11,720 --> 00:05:12,830
He looks a bit familiar.

102
00:05:16,070 --> 00:05:17,720
Xiao Yan, Little Fairy Doctor,

103
00:05:18,390 --> 00:05:20,510
you both know this person.

104
00:05:21,390 --> 00:05:22,230
Speaking of it,

105
00:05:22,600 --> 00:05:24,550
he was the first person that
Little Fairy Doctor met

106
00:05:24,950 --> 00:05:26,230
when she arrived in Central Plains.

107
00:05:29,000 --> 00:05:31,000
- Ice River Valley Master?
- Ice River Valley Master?

108
00:05:31,480 --> 00:05:32,760
What Ice River Valley Master?

109
00:05:33,040 --> 00:05:34,640
I'm not him. I'm not.

110
00:05:34,790 --> 00:05:36,640
I'm here to deliver something.

111
00:05:36,720 --> 00:05:38,390
After delivering the goods, I'll leave.

112
00:05:38,590 --> 00:05:39,460
Goodbye.

113
00:05:39,480 --> 00:05:40,790
Where are you going?

114
00:05:44,110 --> 00:05:45,160
It's really you.

115
00:05:47,760 --> 00:05:49,760
I—I—I

116
00:05:52,270 --> 00:05:53,720
just wanted to apologize

117
00:05:54,230 --> 00:05:55,670
to Little Fairy Doctor in person.

118
00:05:56,670 --> 00:05:57,720
It was all my fault.

119
00:06:00,320 --> 00:06:01,160
I...

120
00:06:01,320 --> 00:06:03,110
I don't expect everyone to forgive me.

121
00:06:04,200 --> 00:06:06,160
I just want to contribute to Central Plains.

122
00:06:12,640 --> 00:06:13,510
I'll leave now.

123
00:06:19,830 --> 00:06:21,200
The alliance meeting is not over yet.

124
00:06:21,880 --> 00:06:22,720
Where are you going?

125
00:06:24,640 --> 00:06:25,480
Really?

126
00:06:28,950 --> 00:06:29,790
Sit down please.

127
00:06:36,510 --> 00:06:37,350
An alliance

128
00:06:37,790 --> 00:06:38,790
needs a name.

129
00:06:39,270 --> 00:06:40,790
Let's think of a good name.

130
00:06:42,760 --> 00:06:44,790
Our opponent is the Hall of Souls.

131
00:06:45,480 --> 00:06:47,510
The name of alliance
should be better than that.

132
00:06:47,950 --> 00:06:52,070
How about calling it "Heavens Mansion"?

133
00:06:54,640 --> 00:06:55,830
Hall of Souls,

134
00:06:56,600 --> 00:06:57,830
Heavens Mansion.

135
00:06:59,000 --> 00:07:00,830
Heavens also means sky.

136
00:07:02,510 --> 00:07:03,600
How about "Sky Mansion"?

137
00:07:07,640 --> 00:07:08,600
Sky Mansion Alliance.

138
00:07:10,040 --> 00:07:10,880
Good.

139
00:07:11,200 --> 00:07:12,110
Sounds magnificent.

140
00:07:12,170 --> 00:07:13,670
Let's go with "Sky Mansion Alliance."

141
00:07:15,350 --> 00:07:17,230
Now that the alliance is established,

142
00:07:17,480 --> 00:07:18,350
we need to establish rules.

143
00:07:18,670 --> 00:07:19,720
The rules are simple:

144
00:07:20,230 --> 00:07:23,270
there is no distinction between high and low
within the alliance,

145
00:07:23,720 --> 00:07:24,600
all parties are equal.

146
00:07:26,200 --> 00:07:28,390
Central Plains should act together.

147
00:07:28,830 --> 00:07:31,320
Among the alliance factions, teleportation
formations need to be built.

148
00:07:31,330 --> 00:07:32,920
In case of a sudden attack
by the Hall of Souls,

149
00:07:32,950 --> 00:07:35,670
all parties can quickly support each other
through the teleportation formations.

150
00:07:37,480 --> 00:07:38,350
Resist the Hall of Souls

151
00:07:39,070 --> 00:07:40,040
until death.

152
00:07:51,600 --> 00:07:52,440
Brat,

153
00:07:53,000 --> 00:07:54,920
how much do you know about the
Purifying Lotus Demon Flame?

154
00:07:57,320 --> 00:07:58,950
It ranks third
on the Heavenly Flames Ranking.

155
00:08:00,920 --> 00:08:02,950
You still don't have a concept of it.

156
00:08:04,000 --> 00:08:06,040
I know it's particularly powerful.

157
00:08:07,670 --> 00:08:08,600
What do you mean by powerful?

158
00:08:10,950 --> 00:08:13,160
The Fallen Heart Flame can turn into
a python in magma.

159
00:08:13,160 --> 00:08:14,200
Does it count as powerful?

160
00:08:14,950 --> 00:08:17,320
The Three Thousand Burning Flame
can only be subdued by the Dragon Seal.

161
00:08:17,670 --> 00:08:18,830
Does that count as powerful?

162
00:08:20,070 --> 00:08:21,200
What I mean is,

163
00:08:21,230 --> 00:08:22,830
I know it is extremely ruthless.

164
00:08:23,670 --> 00:08:25,830
When trying to tame it,
it's a matter of life and death.

165
00:08:30,480 --> 00:08:32,200
Everything I say is wrong.

166
00:08:33,640 --> 00:08:35,550
Fine, I admit,

167
00:08:36,520 --> 00:08:38,470
I may not know it well.

168
00:08:39,760 --> 00:08:41,550
You need to first admit your ignorance about it

169
00:08:42,030 --> 00:08:43,640
to make better preparations.

170
00:08:44,960 --> 00:08:45,800
You should know that

171
00:08:45,850 --> 00:08:47,440
among the various heavenly flames
in the world,

172
00:08:48,230 --> 00:08:49,470
most of them

173
00:08:49,470 --> 00:08:51,520
were tamed by many masters

174
00:08:52,110 --> 00:08:54,550
and were free after the fall of those masters.

175
00:08:55,350 --> 00:08:57,230
How many leave behind a lasting reputation?

176
00:08:58,710 --> 00:09:00,700
But the Purifying Lotus Demon Flame is different.

177
00:09:01,280 --> 00:09:02,880
It was only tamed by one person.

178
00:09:03,200 --> 00:09:05,910
While alive, this person was a Dou Saint,

179
00:09:06,230 --> 00:09:08,280
and even after falling,
his reputation persisted.

180
00:09:09,200 --> 00:09:10,760
This person
is the Purifying Lotus Demon Saint.

181
00:09:12,440 --> 00:09:13,520
Purifying Lotus Demon Saint.

182
00:09:14,280 --> 00:09:15,880
Purifying Lotus Demon Flame.

183
00:09:16,840 --> 00:09:17,680
That's right.

184
00:09:18,230 --> 00:09:19,580
The Purifying Lotus Demon Saint

185
00:09:19,640 --> 00:09:21,350
named the heavenly flame after himself.

186
00:09:21,910 --> 00:09:22,910
After his fall,

187
00:09:23,280 --> 00:09:25,760
the Purifying Lotus Demon Flame disappeared

188
00:09:26,230 --> 00:09:27,320
from the Dou Qi Continent,

189
00:09:27,590 --> 00:09:29,080
becoming a mystery.

190
00:09:30,110 --> 00:09:31,080
So,

191
00:09:31,710 --> 00:09:33,280
besides the Purifying Lotus Demon Saint,

192
00:09:33,960 --> 00:09:35,790
no one else has tamed
the Purifying Lotus Demon Flame.

193
00:09:37,280 --> 00:09:38,120
Xiao Yan,

194
00:09:38,200 --> 00:09:40,080
with your current level as a Dou Venerate,

195
00:09:40,200 --> 00:09:41,710
trying to tame the Purifying Lotus Demon Flame

196
00:09:42,000 --> 00:09:43,880
is like going to the gates of hell.

197
00:09:45,110 --> 00:09:46,360
Wait for another three years.

198
00:09:46,470 --> 00:09:48,550
And you can try to ascend to a Dou Saint.

199
00:09:49,000 --> 00:09:49,840
Perfect.

200
00:09:49,880 --> 00:09:50,760
Three years?

201
00:09:51,790 --> 00:09:52,960
But... Three years?

202
00:09:53,320 --> 00:09:55,910
Even I can wait,
the Purifying Lotus Demon Flame can't.

203
00:09:56,440 --> 00:09:57,590
Haste makes waste.

204
00:09:57,790 --> 00:09:59,150
You have to become totally different.

205
00:09:59,790 --> 00:10:00,630
It's not just you,

206
00:10:00,840 --> 00:10:02,000
the Gu Clan is the same.

207
00:10:02,350 --> 00:10:04,470
Otherwise, it would be suicide.

208
00:10:07,590 --> 00:10:09,200
Mr. Yao, is there a method

209
00:10:09,320 --> 00:10:10,520
that doesn't take three years?

210
00:10:12,150 --> 00:10:12,990
There is,

211
00:10:13,670 --> 00:10:14,510
but

212
00:10:14,960 --> 00:10:16,880
it's not much different from suicide.

213
00:10:20,520 --> 00:10:22,000
When I broke through to Dou Saint,

214
00:10:22,520 --> 00:10:24,030
I truly experienced

215
00:10:24,030 --> 00:10:26,520
the subtleties and difficulties
of the nine turns

216
00:10:26,910 --> 00:10:29,030
from a peak Dou Venerate to a Dou Saint.

217
00:10:29,790 --> 00:10:32,200
It not only requires a strong and forceful
breakthrough in strength

218
00:10:32,400 --> 00:10:34,780
but also emphasizes enlightenment in
one's mental state.

219
00:10:35,520 --> 00:10:37,570
There's a continuous flow of energy
between heaven and earth.

220
00:10:37,670 --> 00:10:38,640
To break through to Dou Saint,

221
00:10:38,790 --> 00:10:40,670
you need to absorb enormous energy.

222
00:10:40,880 --> 00:10:42,520
Now that you're already a peak Dou Venerate,

223
00:10:43,030 --> 00:10:45,030
there are few pills that can help you
progress further.

224
00:10:46,590 --> 00:10:47,710
The energy required

225
00:10:48,080 --> 00:10:51,640
is more like absorbing heavenly flames
and experiencing life and death.

226
00:10:53,320 --> 00:10:55,440
But where can we find such a place?

227
00:10:56,400 --> 00:10:58,960
When I founded the Starfall Hall in the
Heavenly Star Mountain,

228
00:10:59,110 --> 00:11:00,960
it was because I saw a hidden source of power

229
00:11:01,110 --> 00:11:03,200
in the depths of the mountains,

230
00:11:03,470 --> 00:11:04,880
known as the Yang Flame Ancient Altar.

231
00:11:05,470 --> 00:11:07,320
If you can get support from the Yang Flame,

232
00:11:07,400 --> 00:11:09,230
coupled with the method I will teach you,

233
00:11:09,640 --> 00:11:11,000
perhaps you can give it a try.

234
00:11:12,150 --> 00:11:14,230
But hasn't the Yang Flame of the Ancient Altar

235
00:11:14,470 --> 00:11:15,640
long been extinguished?

236
00:11:17,350 --> 00:11:18,190
Don't you remember?

237
00:11:18,880 --> 00:11:20,280
When your meridians were severed,

238
00:11:20,590 --> 00:11:22,440
Feng Xian reignited the Yang Flame to
save your life.

239
00:11:22,910 --> 00:11:25,550
This proves that the root of the Yang Flame
was not completely severed.

240
00:11:25,910 --> 00:11:28,520
As for whether you can eventually master it,

241
00:11:29,520 --> 00:11:31,320
it depends on whether it accepts you.

242
00:11:35,280 --> 00:11:37,630
The Purifying Lotus Demon Saint was
a member of the Ling Clan.

243
00:11:37,790 --> 00:11:39,880
He just left half of the map
with the Ling Clan,

244
00:11:40,000 --> 00:11:43,080
intending to stop the future generations from
taming the flame.

245
00:11:44,910 --> 00:11:47,700
Near the Purifying Lotus Demon Flame,
there is a Nightmare Heavenly Fog

246
00:11:48,110 --> 00:11:49,760
that can affect human emotions.

247
00:11:50,200 --> 00:11:51,320
Once emotions are stirred,

248
00:11:52,520 --> 00:11:54,910
the Demon Flame will surge within the body

249
00:11:55,320 --> 00:11:57,470
until it incinerates the person
into nothingness.

250
00:11:58,520 --> 00:12:01,110
Therefore, taming the Purifying Lotus
Demon Flame

251
00:12:01,110 --> 00:12:02,840
requires not only breaking through to
the Dou Saint

252
00:12:02,840 --> 00:12:03,680
but also stabilizing

253
00:12:04,280 --> 00:12:06,670
the mind with the power of bloodlines.

254
00:12:07,400 --> 00:12:09,030
Our Gu Clan has a responsibility.

255
00:12:10,470 --> 00:12:12,030
Xun'er has a divine bloodline,

256
00:12:12,470 --> 00:12:15,440
she was supposed to tame
the Purifying Lotus Demon Flame.

257
00:12:16,320 --> 00:12:19,790
However, her body already contains
the Golden Emperor Burning Flame,

258
00:12:20,320 --> 00:12:22,520
making it impossible to acquire
a second heavenly flame.

259
00:12:23,320 --> 00:12:25,520
She can only assist others.

260
00:12:27,640 --> 00:12:28,480
Gu Yao.

261
00:12:31,910 --> 00:12:34,760
We will send out Gu Yao, the Devil General
of the Black Submerged Army,

262
00:12:35,470 --> 00:12:38,400
to take in the Demon Flame
on behalf of the alliance.

263
00:12:39,350 --> 00:12:40,230
Xun'er will assist him.

264
00:12:40,910 --> 00:12:44,030
The two of them will undergo closed-door
cultivation to break through to Dou Saint.

265
00:12:48,910 --> 00:12:49,750
Give it a try,

266
00:12:50,150 --> 00:12:51,110
and see if you can absorb it.

267
00:12:55,670 --> 00:12:56,790
Use the Flame Mantra.

268
00:13:12,200 --> 00:13:14,000
It seems that the Yang Flame has accepted you.

269
00:13:14,960 --> 00:13:15,800
Mr. Yao,

270
